<h2 id="using-impact">Using impact</h2>

<p>The impact component brings together a <a href="/docs/core/elements/hero">hero image</a> and <a href="/docs/core/elements/overlay">overlay</a> to highlight content for news, campaigns and promotions.</p>

<p>It should only be used on the homepage and landing pages that have a campaign focus, such as the news landing page.</p>

<p>It shouldn’t be used on information and topic pages.</p>
:ET